%h4 For legal assistance with your adult record in Cook County (including Chicago):
%ol
  %li
    Get a copy of your Chicago Police arrest record (rap sheet) at:
    %br/
    Records and Services Division of the Chicago Police Department:
    %br/
    3510 S Michigan, Chicago IL 60653
    %br/
    (312)745-5508
    %br/
    Mon-Fri 8am-12pm
    %br/
    Note: it costs $16 to get your adult rap sheet
    *if you were arrested outside Chicago, contact the police department that arrested you to find out how to get your records
  %li
    Bring your rap sheet to Cabrini Green Legal Aid's Adult Expungement Help Desk:
    %br/
    Daley Center
    %br/
    50 W Washington, Room 1006
    %br/
    Chicago, IL 60602
    %br/
    Mon, Tues, Wed, Thurs: 9am-12pm
    %br/
    Thurs: 1pm-4pm
    %br/
    *you should arrive before 9am or before 1pm to get assistance, since space is limited
%br/
